*mousetweaks-2.24.0 (19 Oct 2008)

  19 Oct 2008; Gilles Dartiguelongue <eva@gentoo.org>
  +mousetweaks-2.24.0.ebuild:
  New version for GNOME 2.24. Mostly bug fixes.

  25 Sep 2008; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> mousetweaks-2.22.3.ebuild:
  Stable for HPPA (bug #236971).

  28 Aug 2008; Gilles Dartiguelongue <eva@gentoo.org>
  -mousetweaks-2.22.1.ebuild, -mousetweaks-2.22.2.ebuild:
  clean up old revisions.

  12 Aug 2008; Raúl Porcel <armin76@gentoo.org> mousetweaks-2.22.3.ebuild:
  alpha/ia64/sparc stable wrt #229709

  10 Aug 2008; Markus Meier <maekke@gentoo.org> mousetweaks-2.22.3.ebuild:
  x86 stable, bug #229709

  30 Jul 2008; Brent Baude <ranger@gentoo.org> mousetweaks-2.22.3.ebuild:
  Marking mousetweaks-2.22.3 ppc stable for bug 229709

  26 Jul 2008; Olivier Crête <tester@gentoo.org> mousetweaks-2.22.3.ebuild:
  Stable on amd64, bug #229709

